<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><br>
Vendui Lady Auryla,<br>
<br>
i have read through the note left in our halls, and decided to send you a short reply. The two questions that worry you are easily answered. <br>
<br>
The fact that you are indeed a halfbreed will make it more of a challenge for you to convince those within the scythe that follow the hard path of your dedication to our cause. As such, it would be wrong to say it will not be 'detrimental', as you put the question.<br>
