<br>
Ssakas sighed deeply.  He sat at his desk, attempting to occupy his mind with the business of the Scythe.  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Half elven warrior of Innorukk.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
His eyes darted to the carafe of wine, breathing on his desk, on the crystal goblets residing beside, one for each Derin and himself.  He took a deep breath, attempting to calm his nerves, and the emotion flowing through his veins.  He shakily picked up a quill, and in sloppy Teir'dal, penned this missive.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Lady Auryla,<br>
<br>
