<br>
~Ssakas Chaigidel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bharvestersofdarkness.showUserPublicProfile?gid=traelle>Traelle</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.cpmission.com/graphics/icons/icon22.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Troublemaker</span><br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(4/24/03 11:54 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A young Warrioress of Innorukk</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:fuchsia;">Traelle cringed, from her place in the hallway of the Halls, as she heard shattering glass from Ssakas' room.<br>
